short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Opens a printable version of an Azure DevOps work item description

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Currently, Microsoft doesn't provide a method of generating printer-friendly versions DevOps work items.  This extension will open a new tab with a printable version of whatever work item you're looking at.  Simply open the work item in Chrome and click the pinned extension button.
